&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Santa Cruz Warriors need a hardworking, committed, and ambitious sales person to join the front office in selling group tickets. In this role, you will be responsible for selling and servicing new group sales accounts, generating new ideas to drive ticket sales, and performing basic office functions as needed. This position reports directly to the Director of Ticket Sales and Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
