&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This is a full-time position and is based in Santa Cruz, CA.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
