&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a proactive and professional Coordinator to support the public relations initiatives of the NBA G League, the Santa Cruz Warriors, and external events at Kaiser Permanente Arena. In this role, you will craft all written communications for the team and develop professional relationships with local media groups throughout Santa Cruz and Monterey Counties. Additionally, you will work closely with the Community Relations team and across all departments. This role reports directly to the Director, Community and Public Relations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
