&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Golden State Community Foundation is looking for a strategic, collaborative, and results-oriented Director to lead the Foundation&#39;s fundraising strategy, operational excellence, and organizational execution. In this role, you will drive philanthropic revenue growth while overseeing the operational infrastructure that enables the Foundation&#39;s community impact initiatives, signature events, and strategic partnerships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
